[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]


Morning guys! U know wat time it is xDDD its me again! I wish u all have enjoyed ur winter days (with snow) bc theres only one January 2024 :))))) Just like Dec 2023, i also hav got plenty of things to do ;) so i was hoping that all these artworks would be finished nicely… Well at least ive put quite some thoughts into them :DDDDD and i think that will do?? Whatever, i hope u like them! 

(not gonna sort them this time, seems meaningless :p sooo lets just start over here!)



[[=]]
[[size 150%]]**//******//**[[/size]]
[[/=]]


[[image 
https://s11.ax1x.com/2024/03/01/pFwxUv6.jpg]]

[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[=]]
//**Merchants’ Style**//

//{{For business… and shooting… and dirty tricks.}}//
[[/=]]
[[/div]]
There’s always a new character design shows up and it’s VKTM for this time. The original author [[*user Grigori Karpin]] has written lots of great stuffs for them and luckily they are still updating. All those works are so entertaining to read and think :) They are such a fascinating GoI and I just can’t hold back my passion to draw them xD! I feel interesting to consider them as a robot but I have had no time to finish a formal design painting, so bear with me! It will pop up next month I suppose :3


[[=]]
[[size 150%]]**//******//**[[/size]]
[[/=]]

[[image https://s11.ax1x.com/2024/03/01/pFwxQDU.jpg]]

[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[=]]
//**The Revelation of Ion**//

//{{It’s our last hope to seize the redemption. }}//
[[/=]]
[[/div]]
This is actually an experimental piece. I went clueless when I was designing the deity form(dunno whether this is the proper phrase) of Ion and it just took forever to rethink it. Still I assume this experiment would continue next month since I’m not very pleased with the result.


[[=]]
[[size 150%]]**//******//**[[/size]]
[[/=]]

[[image https://s11.ax1x.com/2024/03/01/pFwxuvV.jpg]]

[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[=]]
//**The Valentine Dessert Recommended**//

//{{A recommendation from Chef Ambrose. You know it’s his duty to provide a decent atmosphere, therefore, he tried hard.}}//
[[/=]]
[[/div]]
Yes its blood. Def blood.Trust me n trust him. :d



[[=]]
[[size 150%]]**//******//**[[/size]]
[[/=]]

[[image https://s11.ax1x.com/2024/03/01/pFwxng0.jpg]]

[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[=]]
//**Time Passes By**//

//{{One day Iris would like to receive her retirement in the dark, leaving all the golden antiques covered with shimmering dust.}}//
[[/=]]
[[/div]]
Guess whos missing her already? ;)))


So thats all for this month! I know ive said it the last time but u know… next month will just be the same xPPP I wish u all enjoyed!!! I love u guys(as always!) and cheers to the busy winter time!!! :DDDDD
